==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Navigator
<hw>Nav"i*ga`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who navigates
or sails; esp., one who direct the course of a ship, or one who is
skillful in the art of navigation; also, a book which teaches the art of
navigation; <as>as, Bowditch's <ex>Navigator</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Navigerous</ent>⟦br⟧
